         <div type="translation" resp="#cmr" xml:lang="en">
            <p><note>i</note>: Iin this tomb lies the body of Abbot Petrus, monk, of good memory. He lived in peace more or less 75 years. 
               He departed from this world on day 21, indiction 10. May the Lord give you rest eternal and may light perpetual shine on you by the indulgence <supplied reason="subaudible">of God</supplied>.</p>
            <p><note>ii</note>: Holy, Holy, Holy, Lord God Sabaoth</p>
            <p><note>iii</note>: Holy, Holy.</p>
